title: JITSymbol::getAddress() returned an error: Symbols not found
body:
*Original issue*: https://gitlab.com/lfortran/lfortran/-/issues/660

Hello,

Please I get the following exception whenever I try to run some fortran code with LSFortran on Jupyter Notebook :

LFortran Exception: JITSymbol::getAddress() returned an error: Symbols not found: [ _lfortran_dexp, _lfortran_datanh, _lfortran_dasin, _lfortran_scosh, _lfortran_sacos, _lfortran_cexp, _lfortran_derf, _lfortran_slog, _lfortran_zasinh, _lfortran_dsinh, _lfortran_zacosh, _lfortran_ssinh, _lfortran_dasinh, _lfortran_csqrt, _lfortran_casinh, _lfortran_satanh, _lfortran_zsinh, _lfortran_scos, _lfortran_zatan, _lfortran_dlog, _lfortran_dacosh, _lfortran_datan2, _lfortran_ccosh, _lfortran_ztanh, _lfortran_dsin, _lfortran_zcos, _lfortran_zexp, _lfortran_dacos, _lfortran_clog, _lfortran_catan, _lfortran_ssin, _lfortran_ctan, _lfortran_catanh, _lfortran_sasinh, _lfortran_datan, _lfortran_zcosh, _lfortran_sexp, _lfortran_sasin, _lfortran_zlog, _lfortran_zasin, _lfortran_zatanh, _lfortran_serf, _lfortran_cacosh, _lfortran_csin, _lfortran_csinh, _lfortran_dcosh, _lfortran_dtanh, _lfortran_ztan, _lfortran_zsin, _lfortran_zsqrt, _lfortran_stan, _lfortran_dtan, _lfortran_sacosh, _lfortran_zacos, _lfortran_stanh, _lfortran_casin, _lfortran_dcos, _lfortran_ctanh, _lfortran_satan, _lfortran_satan2, _lfortran_ccos, _lfortran_cacos ]

None of the Fortran intrinsic functions are working. I don't know how to go about this.
